{
  "stem": "27335.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then many of them started in an exodus back, and many, many of them settled [? in the ?] north-- in the north in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes-- and we're politically, I just counted up not very long ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the, uh, the uh, grocery store-- and the pubs and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of the-- some of the tradesmens, and so there were all together about-- a little over 50-- between 50 and 60 in the village, like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were-- there were the Goldstein, there were-- there were Gross and Klein, and Klein was a small holder.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He rented about 100 acres above land, there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a hard part to remember-- remember the names anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, he was-- he was a thin maker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Santo ?] was the-- Hungarian Jews, I have to inject this, were the most assimilated among all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to claim that it was Germany-- no, it wasn't Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was Hungary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And almost half of the of the village Jews had Hungarian names.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And many of them, well not so many converted, but the mixed marriages, eh, Christian Hungarians married into-- into Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were reasons-- first of all, they were, as being merchant tradesmen, and so on-- they were well-kept, so to say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were handsome, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I had a-- [LAUGHS] when I was in high school, my first real girlfriend was a Jew-- a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almost across the road, he was a butcher in-- in-- [INAUDIBLE], among the three.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you remember her name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ella.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she's-- well, they, then they immigrated to Canada, settled only in Hamilton.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, then I ran into her once-- in one kind of gathering, in a synagogue, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
